r />\n新到書：良臻《逆權教師》<br />\n作者：良臻(楊子俊)<br />\n出版社：山道出版社<br />\n售價：$138  會員價：$117.30<br />\n612中槍後，<br />\n他開始了校內與社會上的雙重分裂生活&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n踩盡教育界的紅線和地雷<br />\n──《端傳媒》<br />\n現實社會上諸多的不公平、不公義，背後又有多少道理可言？<br />\n「可以改變的&hellip;&hellip;或者是我們作出的選擇。」<br />\n屋邨名校、熱血男校、精英女校、通識、出版、社會運動、議會選舉、傳媒&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n香港教師楊子俊歷練8年的現實故事。<br />\n【作者簡介】<br />\n良臻<br />\n真名楊子俊，香港出生、香港長大。<br />\n熱衷於電腦科技，香港大學社會科學學士。<br />\n通識科教師、出版人，曾於中學任教8年。<br />\n2019年6月12日於示威現場中彈，積極參與社會運動，以「良臻」為筆名推動出版自由"},{"pid":"44157e13bba1a6942de5c7321497e77c2b14c3c4","tid":2247386,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T01:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3176bb6b1baa75c3bf0a22b7979c4c735c300dad","tid":2247386,"uid":34457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T01:33:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"74ef1351ad663ca213ee20aa514400035bc96a42","tid":2247386,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T02:23:43.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a031ae457003cd8a8cbcef0ee2a2fcf37afa83","tid":2247386,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T02:39:27.000Z","msg":"仲等緊本書...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bb3c5dd05ed06081a7e2ebae5c3ff66412b924","tid":2247386,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"冇錯, 政府唔比你出聲, 你咪寫書囉; 政府唔比你出書, 你咪投稿登報紙專欄囉; 政府唔比你登報, 你咪上獅子山掛旗囉; 政府唔比你上獅子山, 你咪去九龍公園做皇帝寫大字囉; 政府唔比你寫大字, 你咪....................................<img src=\"/assets/fa